This is a Processing sketch demonstrating the barycentric method for testing if a point is inside of a triangle.

You will need Processing in order to run the sketch:
http://www.processing.org

This sketch is modelled after the flash example on Black Pawn:
http://www.blackpawn.com/texts/pointinpoly/default.html

Instructions:
Move mouse to demonstrate point in triangle detection
Click mouse to generate a new triangle

